    "title": "Fee-on-transfer tokens can drain accumulated reserves because spending is based on nominal input, not actual receipt",
    "locations": [
      "onchain_auto/0x3335a88bb18fd3b6824b59af62b50ce494143333/contracts/RubicProxy.sol:69",
